name: ▥▬┋ Weaving
description:
One of a kind textile wall hanging constructed on a frame loom in Kayla Mattes' studio in Portland, OR. This hand woven tapestry is made with a combination of recycled Pendleton wool and reclaimed yarns (cotton, wool, mohair, nylon, iridescent polyester). Metal rings are attached to the back of the textile for wall attachment.

12 x 7" inches

Weaving commissions are welcomed: contact@kaylamattes.com
